Install the CRM Sample Dashboards from AppExchange

The CRM sample dashboards package from AppExchange offers best-practice dashboards with underlying reports that are based on your organization’s standard objects and fields. You can use these sales, marketing, service, and support dashboards to track business processes and key performance metrics for yourself, your team, and your company.

Sales & Marketing Dashboards
Marketing Executive Dashboard
Sales Executive Dashboard
Sales Manager Dashboard
Salesperson Dashboard
Customer Service Dashboards
Agent Supervisor Overview Dashboard
Service Executive Overview Dashboard
Service KPIs Dashboard

To install the sample dashboards, search for “Salesforce CRM Dashboards” in AppExchange and click Get It Now.
title: Installing CRM Sample Dashboards on Salesforce
